::Zardus/etc...::

All the bots that phased out thursday suddenly phase back in.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Zardus lands in the alliance base, extremely mad. He had seen everything that 
went on with the alliance from where he was phased out. He opens a comm-link 
to Nemesis. "Nemesis, return to base. Whatever Wolfgang did was a mistake."

He turns to Wolfgang, "I suppose you'd like to tell me why you shot him?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Shredder appears in a red light and sets off after Megatron.
